regions.text:
Father, we miss you everywhere,
Miss your advice, love and care;
A faithful father, king and true,
We always pray and think of you.
You are not forgotten in our minds.
To us you were so good and kind;
How our hearts are filled with pain,
We hope some day we will meet again.

How we miss you no one knows,
Rest on dear one, thy labor is oer;
Thy willing hands will toll no more.
We know that you are happy;
In the mansion of the blest,
Where there is no pain or sorrow;
In one sweet eternal rest.
